script.name: !init.ship.globalscriptmap.pl
script.description: Initialisation for all ships with race player
script.sourceplaintext:
* ............................................................. * set default scripts for all ships with race player * .............................................................
$race = Player * Navigation Commands global script map: ignore: key=COMMAND_IDLE, class=Fighter Drone, race=$race global script map: ignore: key=COMMAND_DOCKAT, class=Fighter Drone, race=$race
global script map: ignore: key=COMMAND_DOCKAT, class=Recon Drone, race=$race
global script map: set: key=COMMAND_FOLLOW, class=Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.follow.pl, prio=0
$cmd = COMMAND_MOVE_SECTOR global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.movesector.pl, prio=0
$cmd = COMMAND_MOVE_POS global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.moveposition.pl, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Fighter Drone, race=$race global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Freight Drone, race=$race
$cmd = COMMAND_MOVEPOSCONTINUE global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.moveposcontinue.pl, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Freight Drone, race=$race
global script map: ignore: key=COMMAND_MOVE_COORDS, class=Freight Drone, race=$race
$cmd = COMMAND_JUMP_STATION global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Moveable Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.jumpstation.std, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Drone, race=$race
$cmd = COMMAND_JUMP_SECTOR global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Moveable Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.jump.std, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Drone, race=$race
$cmd = COMMAND_JUMP_POSITION global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Moveable Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.jumpposition.std, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Drone, race=$race
global script map: ignore: key=COMMAND_JUMPTOME, class=Freight Drone, race=$race
* Trade Commands $cmd = COMMAND_GET_WARE global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.getware.pl, prio=0 global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Freight Drone, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.getware.drone.pl, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Huge Ship, race=$race
$cmd = COMMAND_GET_WARE_BEST global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.getwarebest.pl, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Drone, race=$race global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Huge Ship, race=$race
$cmd = COMMAND_SELL_WARE global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.sellware.pl, prio=0 global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Freight Drone, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.sellware.drone.pl, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Huge Ship, race=$race
$cmd = COMMAND_SELL_WARE_BEST global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.sellwarebest.pl, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Drone, race=$race global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Huge Ship, race=$race
$cmd = COMMAND_TRADE_MINE global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Drone, race=$race
$cmd = COMMAND_FREIGHT_TRANSFER global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Drone, race=$race
* preload, but needs .pl-script $cmd = COMMAND_MANUAL_TRADE_RUN global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Moveable Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.mtc.trade.run.pl, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Drone, race=$race
$cmd = COMMAND_REMOTE_BESTBUY global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Moveable Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.mtc.bestbuy.pl, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Drone, race=$race
$cmd = COMMAND_REMOTE_BESTSELL global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Moveable Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.mtc.bestsell.pl, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Drone, race=$race
* Fight Commands $cmd = COMMAND_PROTECT global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.protect.pl, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Freight Drone, race=$race global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Recon Drone, race=$race
$cmd = COMMAND_ATTACK global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.attack.pl, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Freight Drone, race=$race global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Recon Drone, race=$race
$cmd = COMMAND_ATTACK_TARGET global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.attacktarget.pl, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Freight Drone, race=$race global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Recon Drone, race=$race
$cmd = COMMAND_ATTACK_SAME global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.attacksame.pl, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Drone, race=$race
$cmd = COMMAND_ATTACK_NEAREST global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.attacknearest.pl, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Freight Drone, race=$race global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Recon Drone, race=$race
$cmd = COMMAND_ATTACK_FIGHTERS global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Freighter, race=$race global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Drone, race=$race
$cmd = COMMAND_ATTACK_BIGSHIPS global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Freighter, race=$race global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Drone, race=$race
global script map: ignore: key=COMMAND_KILL_ENEMIES, class=Freight Drone, race=$race global script map: ignore: key=COMMAND_KILL_ENEMIES, class=Recon Drone, race=$race
$cmd = COMMAND_KILL_ENEMIES_RANGE global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Moveable Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.killenemiesrange.pl, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Freight Drone, race=$race global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Recon Drone, race=$race
$cmd = COMMAND_KILL_ENEMIES_AND_LAND global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.killenemiesland.pl, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Drone, race=$race global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Big Ship, race=$race
$cmd = COMMAND_DEFEND_STATION global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Moveable Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.defend.station.pl, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Drone, race=$race
$cmd = COMMAND_ATTACK_RETURN global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.attackreturn.pl, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Drone, race=$race global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Big Ship, race=$race
$cmd = COMMAND_ATTACK_BOARDSHIP global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=M3, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.boardship.pl, prio=0 global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=TP, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.boardship.pl, prio=0 global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Big Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.boardship.pl, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=M7D, race=$race global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=M8, race=$race global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=TL, race=$race global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=TM, race=$race global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=M1, race=$race global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Drone, race=$race
$cmd = COMMAND_LAUNCH_ALLMARINES global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=M3, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.launchmarines.pl, prio=0 global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=TP, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.launchmarines.pl, prio=0 global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Big Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.launchmarines.pl, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=M7D, race=$race global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=TL, race=$race global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=M8, race=$race global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=TM, race=$race global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=M1, race=$race global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Drone, race=$race
$cmd = COMMAND_DEPLOY_FIGHTERS global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Ship, race=$race global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=TM, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.deployfighters.std, prio=0
$cmd = COMMAND_RETREAT global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Moveable Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.retreat.std, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Drone, race=$race
* Special Commands $cmd = COMMAND_COLLECT_WARE global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.collectware.std, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Big Ship, race=$race global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=M6, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.collectware.std, prio=0 global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=TM, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.collectware.std, prio=0
$cmd = COMMAND_COLLECT_ASTRONAUT global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.collectastronaut.pl, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Drone, race=$race global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Big Ship, race=$race global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=M6, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.collectastronaut.pl, prio=0 global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=TM, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.collectastronaut.pl, prio=0
$cmd = COMMAND_COLLECT_FLYINGWARES global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.collectflyingwares.pl, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Big Ship, race=$race global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=M6, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.collectflyingwares.pl, prio=0 global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=TM, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.collectflyingwares.pl, prio=0
$cmd = COMMAND_MINE_AUTO global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Drone, race=$race
$cmd = COMMAND_MINING_DEBRIS global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Moveable Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.mineminerals.pl, prio=0
* Explorer Commands $cmd = COMMAND_DEPLOY_SATS global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Moveable Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.deploysats.pl, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Drone, race=$race
$cmd = COMMAND_EXPLORE_SECTOR global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Moveable Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.mapsector.pl, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Freight Drone, race=$race
$cmd = COMMAND_FLYTHROUGH_GATE global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Moveable Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.passgate.pl, prio=0 global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Astronaut, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.passgate.pl, prio=0 *global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Freight Drone, race=$race
$cmd = COMMAND_SCAN_ASTEROID global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Moveable Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.scan.roid.pl, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Freight Drone, race=$race global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Recon Drone, race=$race
* Supply Commands $cmd = COMMAND_EQUIPLIKE global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Moveable Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.resupply.equiplike.pl, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Drone, race=$race
$cmd = COMMAND_REARM global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Moveable Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.resupply.rearm.pl, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Drone, race=$race
$cmd = COMMAND_REFUEL global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Moveable Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.resupply.fueler.pl, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Drone, race=$race
* preload, but needs .pl-script $cmd = COMMAND_RESUPPLY global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Moveable Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.resupply.group.pl, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Drone, race=$race
* Drone Commands $cmd = COMMAND_RECON_MAPSECTOR global script map: set: key=$cmd, class=Moveable Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.cmd.mapsector.drones.pl, prio=0 global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Drone, race=$race
* Signals global script map: set: key=SIGNAL_ATTACKED, class=Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.signal.attacked, prio=100 global script map: set: key=SIGNAL_ATTACKED, class=TS, race=$race, script=!ship.signal.attacked, prio=100 global script map: set: key=SIGNAL_BUYWARE, class=Station, race=$race, script=!station.signal.buyware, prio=100 global script map: set: key=SIGNAL_SELWARE, class=Station, race=$race, script=!station.signal.sellware, prio=100 global script map: set: key=SIGNAL_NONE, class=Moveable Ship, race=$race, script=!ship.signal.cmdnone.pl, prio=100
global script map: set: key=SIGNAL_LOADWARE, class=TL, race=$race, script=!tl.signal.loadware, prio=100 global script map: set: key=SIGNAL_UNLOADWARE, class=TL, race=$race, script=!tl.signal.unloadware, prio=100 global script map: set: key=SIGNAL_WARETRANSFER, class=TL, race=$race, script=!tl.signal.transferware, prio=100 global script map: set: key=SIGNAL_HQ_WARERECYCLED, class=Headquarters, race=$race, script=!station.signal.recycled, prio=100
* Ignore Jobs global script map: ignore: key=COMMAND_INVASION, class=Ship, race=$race global script map: ignore: key=COMMAND_PATROL, class=Ship, race=$race global script map: ignore: key=COMMAND_PREACH, class=Ship, race=$race global script map: ignore: key=COMMAND_WAR_DEFENDSECTOR, class=Ship, race=$race global script map: ignore: key=COMMAND_WAR_INVADESECTORS, class=Ship, race=$race return null

comment.var: set default scripts for all ships with race player

line.comment: *global script map: ignore: key=$cmd, class=Freight Drone, race=$race

sval.val: Initialisation for all ships with race player
set default scripts for all ships with race player
